          "_name": "info3",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"info3\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" plugins=\"mobirise-icons2\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background4.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#232323\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#4479d9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.6\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"card col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box align-center\">\n                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-box\">\n                            <b>Home Team</b></h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-box .mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                            2500+ beautiful website blocks, templates and themes help you start easily.</p>\n                        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnAdd, -mbrBtnMove, -mbrBtnRemove\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\">\n                            <a class=\"btn btn-warning\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Buy\n                                Mobirise Kit</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_cid": "vjD3MS2xov",
          "_anchor": "info3-79",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor"
          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><b>Meet the players...</b></h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">Hastings Athletic</h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Soheil 1 - Soheil is a fantastic shot stopper learning his trade<br><br>Ashton 2 - Ash can play anywhere on the pitch, he has a free kick second to none and is a guaranteed starter of CB due to his great reading of the game.<br><br>Rahim 66 - Rahim is a classic captain, a rock at CB with the aerial prowess of a salmon !<br><br>Stanley.O 5 - A dynamic fullback and set piece specialist for his corners, his long legs seek out the ball in tackles.<br><br>Liam 'macca ' 9 - Macca is a jack and master of all trades ,he plays well in every position on the pitch and never gives up.<br><br>Dylan 99 - Dylan is a new member of our team this season , he comes in offering versatility and much needed enthusiasm<br><br>Liam 'welchie' 32 - Fullback/striker extraordinaire , best attitude on the pitch and gives110% wherever he plays <br><br>Isaac 'Ike@ 4 -tenacious defensive midfielder ,does the job no one else wants , one of the first names on the team sheet<br><br>Mo 11- Mo passes like Pirlo and tackles like Roy Keane ! what more could you ask for in a centre midfielder<br><br>Stanley.S 10- Stanley is our teams dream player and every other teams nightmare ! A great future star <br><br>Louie 19 - Louie is the ultimate professional, he always does the job he is asked to do and he has the ability to play any position <br><br>Flavio 77 - Flavio arrives on his own time ,but when he does he brings his unbelievable silky footwork and dynamic one touch passes   <br><br>Mark 8 - Marky is our very own Maradona, he terrifies defences and he has an unbelievable work rate to match <br><br>Jack 7 - Jack leads the line like a spartan charging into battle ! he scores with his right , he scores with his left and with his incredible headers<br><br>Mazen 26 - Mazen has a great turn of foot and vision of passing to match , despite being tall you don't play to him you play through him ! <br><br>Rosie 6 - Due to an enforced injury Rosie is unable to play this match. However , when she does play there is no body stronger. No body  that works harder and no body more determined <br><br>George 3 - Again injury has forced George out of this game, however his calm presence and ball playing prowess will be missed at the heart of our defence&nbsp;<br><br><br><br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vjD3MSaGZX",
          "_anchor": "content5-7a",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
