          "_name": "info3",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"info3\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" plugins=\"mobirise-icons2\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background4.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#232323\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#4479d9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.6\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"card col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box align-center\">\n                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-box\">\n                            <b>Home Team</b></h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-box .mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                            2500+ beautiful website blocks, templates and themes help you start easily.</p>\n                        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnAdd, -mbrBtnMove, -mbrBtnRemove\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\">\n                            <a class=\"btn btn-warning\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Buy\n                                Mobirise Kit</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_cid": "uHks2l7wKK",
          "_anchor": "info3-6e",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor"
          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><b>Meet the players...</b></h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">AS Eastbourne</h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Lewis Richardson<br>A long-standing member of All Stars, Lewis has shown outstanding development over the years. His growth has made him a key and reliable player within the squad.<br><br>Reggie Stewart<br>A long-time player and team captain, Reggie leads by example. He combines strong technical ability with excellent tactical understanding, making him central to the team's success.<br><br>Tommy Nones<br>Tommy has taken significant strides over the past 12 months, emerging as a leader within the group. His improvement has been clear and impactful.<br><br>Matthew Oakey<br>Matthew has improved greatly and offers valuable versatility across multiple positions. His technical quality and tactical awareness stand out.<br><br>Max Clarke<br>Quick, powerful, and blessed with a strong left foot, Max plays beyond his years. Despite being U14, he is an important contributor at U15 level.<br><br>Vincent Wiley<br>A technically gifted player who plays a key role in helping the team build and control play. His influence is vital to the team's style.<br><br>Harrison Fry<br>Technically excellent, Harrison has the ability to create chances with his skill on the ball and is a constant attacking threat.<br><br>Oliver Hole<br>Extremely quick and dynamic, Oliver has contributed numerous important goals and assists this season, making a big impact in attack.<br><br>Jayden Jones<br>An intelligent player with strong technical and tactical qualities. Jayden's versatility allows him to perform effectively in multiple positions.<br><br>Oscar Ramsden<br>A physically strong and dependable player who contributes both in defence and midfield. His technical ability continues to improve steadily.<br><br>Joel Stripp<br>Joel has made great technical progress since joining All Stars. His adaptability across various positions adds real value to the team.<br><br>Sonny Tucker<br>A powerful and fast attacking player who makes a noticeable difference when on the pitch. His presence brings energy and threat going forward.<br><br>Rory Purvis<br>A very capable goalkeeper who not only makes excellent saves but is also comfortable playing with his feet, aiding the team's build-up play.<br><br>Henry Smith<br>A prolific goal scorer since joining at the start of the season. Henry's pace and dynamism, combined with his continual improvement, make him a major asset.<br><br>Matei Foca<br>Technically strong with a solid understanding of the game, Matei contributes intelligently in possession and in overall play.<br><br>Ben Batchelor<br>A strong and reliable defender with a good reading of the game. Ben's physicality and understanding make him tough to beat.<br><br>Freddie Harrison<br>Technically skilled and tactically aware, Freddie's intelligence and versatility allow him to perform well in a range of positions.<br><br>Jacob Temmerman-Smith<br>Quick, strong, and physically impressive, Jacob competes extremely well and brings intensity and determination to the team.<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "uHks2lfI4w",
          "_anchor": "content5-6f",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor"
