          "_name": "info3",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"info3\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" plugins=\"mobirise-icons2\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background4.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#232323\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#4479d9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.6\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"card col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box align-center\">\n                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-box\">\n                            <b>Home Team</b></h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-box .mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                            2500+ beautiful website blocks, templates and themes help you start easily.</p>\n                        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnAdd, -mbrBtnMove, -mbrBtnRemove\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\">\n                            <a class=\"btn btn-warning\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Buy\n                                Mobirise Kit</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_cid": "uGWRCiulvU",
          "_anchor": "info3-1w",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor"
          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><b>Meet the players...</b></h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">Ringmer Rovers</h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\"Ringmer Rovers Raiders<br><br>1. Louis Ball<br>Signed from today‚Äôs opponents, Louis has been outstanding since arriving. A fearless shot-stopper, calm with the ball at his feet, and a commanding presence who gives real confidence to those in front of him.<br><br>2. Zac Sharp<br>A revelation this season after stepping out from goal into central defence. Strong, quick, and composed in possession, with an eye for a pass from the back.<br><br>4. Jaxon Partridge<br>A superb season following his move into attacking midfield. Now the Raiders‚Äô top goalscorer with 15 goals, including two hat-tricks ‚Äî a transition that couldn‚Äôt have gone better.<br><br>6. Tom McEntee<br>Back to his best this season. Relentless, tenacious, and never beaten easily ‚Äî any winger facing Tom knows they‚Äôre in for a tough afternoon.<br><br>7. Archie Crane<br>Endless energy and drive. Equally strong on both feet, always willing to take players on and play his part in creating goals.<br><br>8. Sam Riches<br>Vice-captain and a leader in every sense. After a slow return from pre-season injury, he‚Äôs hit top form at exactly the right time. One of the league‚Äôs standout central midfielders when on song.<br><br>9. Freddy Lawrence<br>Composed beyond his years. Always seems to have time on the ball, reads the game brilliantly, and rarely makes the wrong decision ‚Äî a coach‚Äôs dream.<br><br>10. Charlie Burman<br>Adapting superbly to a new role this season, operating as a number 10 or wide midfielder. Calm in possession, rarely loses the ball, and sees passes others don‚Äôt.<br><br>12. Felix Hermann<br>Limited appearances this season, but always makes an impact. A quality goalkeeper who is just as comfortable stepping into midfield when needed.<br><br>16. Barnaby Green<br>Captain and heartbeat of the team. Tireless, determined, and sets the standard. When Ba performs, the Raiders perform.<br><br>23. Cody Sage<br>A superb addition this season. Powerful, dominant in the air, composed on the ball ‚Äî a complete player. Could be key today.<br><br>25. Charlie Treagus<br>Mr Versatile. Wherever he plays, he delivers. Strong, skilful, hard-working, and always a goal threat.<br><br>27. Dougie Patterson<br>Missing today and a big loss. Strong in the tackle, composed on the ball, and loves the defensive side of the game.<br><br>28. Jake Epps<br>Four goals on debut and hasn‚Äôt looked back. Sharp, creative, and clinical. May lack size, but more than makes up for it with skill and determination.<br><br>29. Barney Hart<br>Power, pace, and presence. A dominant defender who‚Äôs tough to beat and a popular figure in the squad ‚Äî just not with opposition forwards.<br><br>38. Harry Burgen<br>A standout season in central midfield. Keeps things ticking with simple, forward play, works tirelessly, and chips in with big goals ‚Äî including a crucial semi-final equaliser.<br><br>72. Max Goodwin<br>Joined to play outfield and hasn‚Äôt looked back. A natural goalkeeper turned dependable left-back ‚Äî determined, two-footed, and always looking to get forward.\"<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "uGWRCklgSD",
          "_anchor": "content5-1x",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor"
          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#bed3f9\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><b>A word from the gaffer...</b></h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"></h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">I's a real privilege to lead the boys into this season's cup final. Having won it in 2023, I know just how special this occasion is and what it means to everyone involved.<br><br>After the disappointment of last season&nbsp; falling short in the league and exiting the cup at the semi-final stage ‚ the boys have responded brilliantly. They'e shown the quality they have when they play with focus, determination, and belief. They are a fantastic group to coach, and today gives them the chance to put last season behind them.<br><br>Congratulations to our opponents, Crowhurst, on reaching the final. They are a strong side who have given us two tough games already this season, and we know we'll need to be at our very best to lift the trophy.<br><br>I'm sure the supporters are in for a great game this evening, played in the right spirit. My thanks, as always, to my fellow coaches and support staff at Ringmer for their continued commitment.<br><br>Let's hope the boys can deliver a performance to be proud of ‚ and bring the cup home.<br><br>Come on Ringmer!<br><br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "uGWRCkSkwo",
          "_anchor": "content5-1y",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
