          "_name": "info3",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"info3\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" plugins=\"mobirise-icons2\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background4.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#232323\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#4479d9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.6\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"card col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box align-center\">\n                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-box\">\n                            <b>Home Team</b></h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-box .mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                            2500+ beautiful website blocks, templates and themes help you start easily.</p>\n                        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnAdd, -mbrBtnMove, -mbrBtnRemove\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\">\n                            <a class=\"btn btn-warning\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Buy\n                                Mobirise Kit</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_cid": "vjD41UAd0G",
          "_anchor": "info3-8b",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor"
          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><b>Meet the players...</b></h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">Hastings United</h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">1 Oscar Jenner, <br>Returning to the team after a year out and it felt like he's never left. His progression this season has been immense providing many saves and the vocal support he gives has made him one of the favourites on and off the pitch.<br><br>76 Oscar Catt,<br>The most consistent performer throughout the season he's always giving everything to the team wherever he plays, his intelligence on and off the ball you can't teach.<br><br>96 Blake Easton-Welby<br>The drive and determination this lad gives on the pitch is to be admired, always turns up on the big occasions and wants to do his best for the team, he's been outstanding the whole season.<br><br>94 Rufus Robertson<br>One of my key midfielders who not only helps his defenders when required but also creates numerous opportunities for others and has bagged a bunch of goals to go with his excellent season.<br><br>84 Evan Baker<br>My RB, the energy level he brings to each and every game is unmatched, always wants to give his all and does!. Always asks did I do good today and it's an easy answer YES! He‚Äôs  been brilliant all season.<br><br>82 Austin Hurd<br>What a player, his ball control and skills has caught the eye of numerous people, the speed and strength to go with it makes him a nightmare on and off the pitch!!!<br><br>34 George Blackman<br>Maybe be one of the smallest but the determination and the fight he gives makes him tower over opponents each and every game. He gives his all every game and has been a stand out performer all season.<br><br>95 Karan Ramadhan<br>Has come up with several crucial goals this season which has helped us get to where we are today, always looking to turn a defender and create space to get his shots off.<br><br>44 Fletter Petter<br>Best cross field passer in the team by far the accuracy and knowledge of when to switch the play has been a nightmare for the opposition. He will never stop running for the cause and is one of the players you want on the ball because you know something's about to happen.<br><br>99 Ronnie Raftery<br>The Joker, has one of the best strikes of the ball I've seen throughout this age group, the strength and ability to quickly release a team mate in behind has been a threat all season.<br><br>93 Herbie Whittle<br>Wow once he's got the ball on the wing 1v1 you just know he's gone. What an outstanding season he's had and h'l be key for us in the final I'm sure. The speed and strength he gives has been a real threat and the assists he creates has made him a players favourite.<br><br>97 Henry Cocker<br>Quiet on and off the field but he hasn't gone unnoticed by me or his teammates, he's formed a brilliant partnership at the back and delivers consistently every game.<br><br>87 Charlie Young Knight<br>Gets stuck in and wants to win every 50/50 can easily change the game when he's given time on the ball and has been an excellent addition to the team this year.<br><br>36 Alex Nieleszczuk<br>The Tank, when he's running at you with the ball at full speed you ain't stopping him. I can play him anywhere and he'll do his best for me and the team.<br><br>56 Stan Gardner<br>The smiler, his infectious attitude to want to have a fun and do his best has been a great addition to the squad. His long throws and relentless aggression has proved vital in key moments of our games.<br><br>48 Leo Bergqvist <br>Captain Leo, unbelievable on and off the ball always there when we need him the most with last ditch tackles and calmness to setup our play. Always wants to give his all to his teammates and be best he can be.\"<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vjD41UJomi",
          "_anchor": "content5-8c",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
