          "_name": "info3",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"info3\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" plugins=\"mobirise-icons2\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background4.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#232323\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#4479d9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.6\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"card col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box align-center\">\n                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-box\">\n                            <b>Away Team</b></h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-box .mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                            2500+ beautiful website blocks, templates and themes help you start easily.</p>\n                        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnAdd, -mbrBtnMove, -mbrBtnRemove\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\">\n                            <a class=\"btn btn-warning\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Buy\n                                Mobirise Kit</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vjD41V5f3W",
          "_anchor": "info3-8f",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor"
          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><b>Meet the players...</b></h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">Ringmer Rovers</h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Freddie Leftley<br>A powerful forward with excellent feet. Holds the ball up superbly and brings teammates into play with clever lay-offs and precision passing, can also find the back of the net<br><br>William Coburn<br>Relentless and full of energy. A tenacious runner who sets the standard for effort and work rate across the team.<br><br>Robin Sweet<br>A committed defender with good pace. Brave and dependable, always willing to put his body on the line.<br><br>Joseph Speed<br>Strong, aggressive, and skilful. A versatile player who can operate in multiple roles and never shies away from a challenge.<br><br>Jack Lloyd<br>The quickest player in the squad. Covers ground effortlessly and makes an impact both defensively and when pressing high.<br><br>Maximus Payne<br>An exciting addition this season. An attacking threat who has already chipped in with important goals.<br><br>Harry Burgan<br>Cool and composed in central midfield. Picks out passes with ease whilst also being a strong aerial presence.<br><br>Ollie Truffet<br>A technically gifted midfielder. Uses quick combinations to escape pressure and drive the team forward. Exquisite range of passing abilities.<br><br>Zachary Roylance<br>A delight to watch in possession. Creative and unpredictable, with the ability to unlock defences and create chances.<br><br>Tristan Taylor<br>Known as ‚ Tristan is a reliable presence at the back. His improved positioning this season has paid off, making him a consistent and dependable defender.<br><br>Patrick Byrne<br>Once the ‚'Utility Man', Patrick has settled into a defensive role on the right. Committed and physical, he thrives on the hard work and isn't afraid to put in a strong challenge.<br><br>Alfie Hills<br>A commanding goalkeeper who leads from the back. Vocal and organised, Alfie has developed his decision-making and distribution, making him a key figure for the team.<br><br>Finlay Matthews<br>A natural athlete who always gives his all. Comfortable in defence or midfield, Finlay also carries a real threat going forward with a powerful strike.<br><br>Alfie Luscombe<br>A vocal leader in the squad. Strong defensively and composed on the ball, Alfie continues to show excellent all-round development.<br><br>Ben Riches<br>A bright addition this season. An attacking midfielder with great balance and vision, always looking to take on opponents and create chances.<br><br>Ben Hilton<br>Quick, strong, and composed under pressure. Ben is a commanding defender who brings confidence and solidity to the back line.\"<br><br><br><br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_cid": "vjD41VgcgO",
          "_anchor": "content5-8g",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor"
          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#bed3f9\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><b>A word from the gaffer...</b></h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"></h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\"It has been both a privilege and a pleasure to work with this group of players and their families. Having only recently joined the coaching setup, I have been made to feel incredibly welcome from the outset.<br><br>This team has been superbly supported and developed by James, Nick, Dan and Terry (who has recently stepped away), whose hard work and guidance laid the foundations for what we see today. Their efforts have made my transition into the role both smooth and enjoyable, and I am extremely grateful for everything they have put in to help guide the team to this cup final.<br><br>The U13s' season has been a mixed one in terms of league results, which at times have not reflected the commitment, attitude and desire shown by the players week in, week out. What has never wavered, however, is their work ethic, togetherness, and willingness to give everything for one another.<br><br>The effort the players have shown to reach this final has been outstanding, and they fully deserve this occasion. With fantastic support from their families, I am certain they will represent themselves and the club with pride today.<br><br>Finally, our congratulations go to Hastings United on reaching the final. We wish them the very best in this evening's fixture and look forward to an entertaining and competitive game.\"<br><br><br><br><br><br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_cid": "vjD41Voih8",
          "_anchor": "content5-8h",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
