          "_name": "info3",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"info3\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" plugins=\"mobirise-icons2\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background4.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#232323\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#4479d9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.6\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"card col-12 col-lg-10\">\n                <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box align-center\">\n                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-box\">\n                            <b>Home Team</b></h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-box .mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                            2500+ beautiful website blocks, templates and themes help you start easily.</p>\n                        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnAdd, -mbrBtnMove, -mbrBtnRemove\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\">\n                            <a class=\"btn btn-warning\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Buy\n                                Mobirise Kit</a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_cid": "uGWZPj0x36",
          "_anchor": "info3-3k",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor"
          },
          "_name": "content5",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content5\" group=\"Content\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"10\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><b>Meet the players...</b></h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">Little Common&nbsp;</h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\"Ernie Freeman - An original member of the team from it first started, a reliable goalkeeper who has makes some fantastic saves when called upon. He communicates well with his defenders giving them good information. <br><br>Ashton Standen - A quiet member of the group with a good knowledge of the game, a reliable defender who is hard to beat and likes to dribble the ball out of defence and set up attacks. <br><br>Rocco Carey - A player who moved up from the colts last season and is solid and dependable defender. He is able to win his duels and use his good range of passing into other team mates. <br><br>Ollie Ballard - Ollie joined us last season and is a good defender who reads the game well with good technical ability to make the right decisions in games. He has a good range of passing and loves a slide tackle. <br><br>Freddie Spice - Freddie joined us last season and started out in midfield but has transitioned into defence, a thoughtful player with a good left foot who can deliver a good ball to his team mates. <br><br>Robert Foord Paton - A player who has great engine working tirelessly in every game, he is strong in a tackle and never lets the opposition rest. Rob likes to try his luck from distance with long shots and is great listener who wants learn. <br><br>Oscar Giles - Oscar joined us last season and has formed a good midfield partnership with Robert. He is composed on the ball and always looking to find the right pass, Oscar is a technical player also scores goals from midfield. <br><br>Leo Shaw  - Leo is a versatile player who can play in a number of positions, he is tenacious and works tirelessly for the team. He is able to drive with the ball and get the team up the pitch as well as making the right decisions when on the ball. <br><br>Harrison Reid - Harrison always has a smile on his face and loves his football. He likes to dribble and take players on to create chances for himself and others, scoring a number of goals throughout the season. <br><br>Rocco Hole - Another original member of the team, who has good feet and dribbling skills to take on players. This often leads for chances for himself and others, he has good technical ability and scores a range of goals from midfield. <br><br>Ralph Conroy Hargrave - Ralph is another original member of the team and is full of energy, he doesn't give the defenders a moment of rest with his pressing, he has developed his game and is a good dribbler who contributes to many goals, including scoring a number himself. <br><br>Hudson Ellis - Hudson joined us this season and showed that he has great ability in front of goal scoring a range of different goals. He has worked hard this season to improve his all round game and this is shown in his performances through the season. \"<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "uGWZPjexHR",
          "_anchor": "content5-3l",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
